Game Logic:
Computer picks a random number between 1 and 100
Player types a guess
The game says: “Too high”, “Too low”, or “Correct!”
Count number of attempts

Step-by-Step Setup
📁 Folder Structure
Create a folder called number-guess-game, then create these files:
number-guess-game/
├── index.html
├── style.css
└── script.js

Open index.html
Right-click → Open with Live Server, or double-click it in File Explorer
Start guessing!
